						               													<description>General info on &amp;quot;Krimi Total&amp;quot;: Murder mystery game in which players act out their role and try to solve the mystery.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Info on this particular case: A group of very young and very successful people (estate agent, bestseller author, actor, pop star, designer, professional boxer, model, exchange student) are invited to a party at a luxurious mansion to celebrate their success stories. Then one of their friends is found dead. What happened? Who is the murderer? This is what the players try to find out through discussions and deduction. The murderer is allowed to lie, all the others have to tell the truth about their characters if asked for information.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In &amp;quot;Party der Intrigen&amp;quot; there are 8 obligatory roles (can't be played with less than 8): 4 male, 4 female. One optional role, the inspector, can be either male or female.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
